      • onProgressUpdate

        void onProgressUpdate(Object url,
                    long total,
                    long downloaded)
        Show download progress.

        This call back method only for download bitmap from the Internet.

        参数:
        url - The URL of the bitmap.
        total - The total size of the downloading bitmap.
        return the download file total size or -1 unknown size.
        downloaded - The downloaded size of the downloading bitmap.

      • onDownloadSuccessed

        void onDownloadSuccessed(Object url,
                       File file)
        Image download successed.

        Only when download image from Internet. if load image from disk cache
        won't call this callback method.

        参数:
        url -
